# Meeting Backgrounds

Low-key virtual backgrounds for Zoom / Teams union meetings. Route: `/tools/meeting-background`.

Distinct from solidarity posters (high-energy board fillers). Keep the centre ~40–50% visually quiet so a webcam face is not fighting type or logos.

## Visual direction
- Soft brand washes (mix primary toward white) — intensity `subtle` | `balanced`
- Colours: Brand Kit primary / secondary / accent only
- Avoid: purple gradients, cream+terracotta, broadsheet layouts, huge centred headlines
- **Export**: PNG only — HD 1920×1080 (default), UHD 3840×2160
- Preview matches export aspect (16:9); flat shadow outside `canvasRef`
- **Export-safe colours**: inside `canvasRef` use inline hex/`rgba` only — no Tailwind colour utilities (oklch washout via html-to-image)
- **Auto ink**: `pickContrastingInk` on wash / panel / bar; pass `backgroundColor` to `BrandLogo`
- No QR / CTA (scanability + clutter behind a face)
- Face silhouette overlay is **preview-only** — never inside `canvasRef`
- No member photos → no ConsentModal
- No union names in presets or core UI — Brand Kit / seed only

## Layouts (face-safe)
1. **Corner** — soft wash; short line + branding bottom-right
2. **Lower third** — quiet bar at bottom; open centre field
3. **Side panel** — narrow left strip (~22%); centre open
4. **Watermark** — very light centred phrase; branding tucked to an edge

## Local branding
Theme established when: onboarding complete, OR official/custom logo set, OR local number non-empty (`isBrandThemeEstablished`).

- Established → “Include local branding” defaults ON
- Not established → toggle OFF; soft link to `/onboarding`
- Always seed canvas colours from Brand Kit

## Presets
Low-key meeting copy in `MEETING_BACKGROUND_PRESETS` (`meeting-background-presets.ts`). Formats in `meeting-background-formats.ts`.
